import cmath

def complex_modulus_diff(a1, b1, a2, b2):
    complex_num1 = complex(a1, b1)
    complex_num2 = complex(a2, b2)
    diff = complex_num1 * complex_num2
    modulus = abs(diff)
    return modulus
